- USe SplitButton for a button that also has a menu on it

### Basic usage

```jsx
<SplitButton
    children="Medium"
    size="medium"
    secondaryDialogContent={
      <SplitButtonMenu id="split-menu">
        <MenuItem icon={Check} title="Hey" />
        <MenuItem icon={Announcement} title="There" />
      </SplitButtonMenu>
    }
  />
  ```

### With Icon

```jsx
<SplitButton
    leftIcon={Add}
    secondaryDialogContent={
      <SplitButtonMenu id="split-menu">
        <MenuItem icon={Check} title="Hey" />
        <MenuItem icon={Announcement} title="There" />
      </SplitButtonMenu>
    }
  >
    Left icon
  </SplitButton>
  ```